Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:05.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想變成屍鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:06.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:09.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你這麼體貼小律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:11.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是屍鬼的幫兇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:21.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:27.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智壽子還是這麼精神 年輕真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:28.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟年輕沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:34.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是經常幫家裡搬米 習慣搬重物而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:35.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經是大嬸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.71,0:00:36.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:40.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智壽子都算大嬸的話那我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:42.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也還算是大嬸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:43.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:47.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這個還在動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:50.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:00:59.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.07,0:01:02.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:04.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都餓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:06.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.64,0:01:10.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 茶葉柱立起來了
