Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:07.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想睡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:13.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 還有我和辰巳先生在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:19.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天一亮 村裡的人肯定就會沖進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:21.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我們就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:26.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心了 快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:30.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這或許就是永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:33.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定再也見不到辰巳和室井先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:36.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不甘心就這樣結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:37.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:39.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 我才不信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:42.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想在沉睡中和你們分別
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:44.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一直醒著 等待那一刻的來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:52.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:54.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:59.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你 讓我對自己稍微有了些瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:00.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:01.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:06.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你告訴我 你為什麼想要自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為絕望了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:14.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本不算答案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:16.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:22.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他就是因為絕望才會殺死自己的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:23.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:27.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟就是連接他和世界的紐帶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:32.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時 也連接著他與絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:36.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我不恨你」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:39.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是這樣對雙目空洞的弟弟說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:42.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我知道」弟弟這樣答道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:45.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這屍鬼第一次開口了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:48.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你讓我擺脫了那裡的束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:52.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是受神支配的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:56.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我為了討神的歡心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:57.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才一直假扮好人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:02.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扼殺自己的本性 卻又厭惡那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:07.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能帶著這份鄙視活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:11.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從心底憎惡這種活法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:15.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和那樣的我完全相反
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:16.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自由自在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:21.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是為什麼弟弟甘願跟隨哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:24.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 弟弟只是想和哥哥在一起罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:26.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:29.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼哥哥會絕望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:35.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 我就是想被你殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:39.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他凝視著弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:41.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 弟弟消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:45.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有到屍鬼該回到墓中的時限
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:50.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 他的弟弟卻消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:55.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他呼喊著弟弟 第一次叫出聲來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:57.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:05:59.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這名字是自己的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:02.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本就沒有弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:07.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人者是他 被殺者也是他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:10.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟是在絕望之中產生的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:14.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他因為這份絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:18.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死了弟弟和他自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:31.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親也對扮演住持的角色絕望了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:39.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也不行嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:48.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 如果就這樣睡著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:54.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 好困
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:07:00.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被殺掉的 像其他同伴那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:05.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:12.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清水 你也被殺了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:16.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是和我在一起 我還能救你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:24.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼我就這麼倒黴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我這麼倒黴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:30.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:40.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:41.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫂子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊 正雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:48.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我吧 我要被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:50.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:54.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有嫂子能救我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:58.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 我會聽話的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是一直都很乖的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:03.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 我不會吸人血的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:06.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我也不會襲擊智香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:09.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證 絕對不會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:11.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說到做到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:13.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 嫂子 求求你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:15.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:16.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫂子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.67,0:08:20.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正雄君 進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:23.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天快亮了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:26.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大概都躲到哪裡去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:27.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:34.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去攻擊想要獵殺我們的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:37.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把老頭老太太也都殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:40.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是為了我們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:53.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:56.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村民們察覺到山入只是時間問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去轉告那裡的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:00.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓人類輕易得手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳枝小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是人狼 所以不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:06.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使一個人 我也會多解決幾個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:09.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天他們會放鬆警惕 或許反而會比較容易下手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:11.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧 太陽就要升起了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:17.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去神社 幹掉年輕醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:22.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 對準他開槍就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:24.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘量離得近一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:34.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正志郎…你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:37.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:38.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:44.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著人狼經過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:05.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能回到村裡了 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:13.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 已經沒地方可埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:16.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕醫生應該會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:19.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不能丟到村子外面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:24.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是去看地獄穴了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:27.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地獄穴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:30.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在主殿后邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:32.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我怎麼沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:33.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過的確是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:39.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把屍體扔進這裡 再把上面弄塌 如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:42.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這樣屍體處理起來會輕鬆很多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去轉告去墓地的人們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:46.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:49.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安代護士來找你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:51.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安代護士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:54.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安代護士 你身上的傷是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:58.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被野狗咬的 還有摔的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:02.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我的運氣還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:04.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:07.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是從山入逃出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:08.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山入？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:14.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡…屍鬼…屍鬼聚集在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:15.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是他們的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:20.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 安代護士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大家集中過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:33.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路被堵住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:37.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 殺光山入的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:40.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始就打算孤立山入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:41.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:47.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安森家應該有油鋸的 誰去把它拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:14.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住持…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:19.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大川先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:26.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以死了 這下子終於可以死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:27.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:31.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你…大川先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:05.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是武藤家的兒子和醫院的小律嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:09.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我用木樁釘死自己的兒子 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:14.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要辭職 請不要管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:19.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的兒子幹出的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:25.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:28.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:31.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿正 桐敷家那兩個還活著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:35.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不解決掉他們 就絕不罷手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:38.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也許已經離開村子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:43.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出村的林道有人把守 國道也封鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:46.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想離開村子恐怕很難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:49.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 山入的人家已經清查過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:51.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:54.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經都殺光了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:56.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:58.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣澤老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:01.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐敷家宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:03.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡應該已經查過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:04.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:07.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那所房子在建造的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多輛卡車運了許多土石出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:15.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定沒錯 那裡肯定有地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:16.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來藏身的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:23.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:27.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室井先生 這裡已經暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:29.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:30.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:32.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村民們要衝進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:37.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 道路都被封鎖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:45.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一條路可走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:51.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能完全遮光 請儘量選擇陰暗的地方走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:57.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室井先生 事到如今還總是麻煩你 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:00.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沙子就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:02.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:04.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去做誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:08.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以問一問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:10.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:14.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要如此效忠沙子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:18.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來 人狼要比屍鬼優秀得多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想說屍鬼是人狼的半成品？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:26.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被千鶴聽到的話 一定會發怒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:30.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道沙子如果聽到剛才的話 又會作何感想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:34.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和物種的優劣無關
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:37.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說是個人感情的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:41.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 沙子她是滅亡的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:45.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲早會迎來滅亡 一切都會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:48.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而沙子卻反抗著 掙扎著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:51.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是被她的精神所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:54.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這很美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:58.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:03.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣 便足夠了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:05.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:28.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉了 快追
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去通知把守國道的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:31.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:32.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他們逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:33.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追 快追
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:09.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退路也不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:43.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕醫生 你看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:44.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:48.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去追 醫生你照看一下受傷的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:48.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.39,0:17:50.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能動的人跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:17:58.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往寺裡去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:17:59.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:01.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個繼續往前找
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:17.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 是剛才那輛車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:23.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車裡沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大川先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:29.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為他們進不了寺院呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:43.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直沒有回來 也不知道到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:47.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就奇怪了 他剛才應該回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:50.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:51.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:54.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是追著他過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:56.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 那我們自己找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:57.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:59.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們把他們藏起來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:02.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺院竟然背叛了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:03.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我搜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:27.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:52.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:19.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主持好像逃進山裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:21.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大川先生他們追過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:22.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:44.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他受傷了 跟著血跡追
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:01.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:40.48,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闇に紛れて 息を殺す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:40.48,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}隱於暗夜 屏住呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:48.08,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闇をまとって ふっと微笑む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:48.08,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}身處暗夜 忽而微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:56.49,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}気のせいさ お前など誰も知るはずない
